                        <p><strong>Accommodation:</strong> Accommodation is as specified in the accommodation section of our websites. All costs are shown in Australian dollars unless otherwise stated. We reserve the right to offer alternative accommodation of a similar standard in case of overbooking or for reasons beyond our control. All rates are subject to change without notice. Not all properties provide instant availability; in such cases, Rahat Travels Of India Pvt. Ltd. checks availability once we receive the booking request.</p>

