                        <p><strong>Check-In/Check-Out Times:</strong> These vary according to the operator. Generally, accommodation check-in is at 2 PM, and check-out is at 10 AM. Most properties will require a credit card authorization on check-in and may need to see photo identification. If you don't have a credit card, usually a cash bond will be required.</p>

